resources.string: Prenesite in namestite dodatne funkcije za ovitek z lučkami LED. Ustvarite lahko svoje ikone LED in jih nastavite kot ikone za obvestila. Če jih želite prenesti pozneje, pojdite v meni Nastavitve > Napredne funkcije > Pripomočki > Ovitek z lučkami LED in izberite možnost Prenos dodatnih funkcij.

Download and install additional features for LED View Cover. You can create your own LED icons and set them as your notification icons. To download them later, go to Settings > Accessories > LED View Cover, then select Download additional features.
